text.en_US: A playful fall fairy spirit who resides deep within the woods of \c[3]\v[area.autumn-dng.name]\c[0]. She is always on the lookout for new playmates to play with in the woods and likes to show off her wind-like agility to her friends. It is said that she usually does not reveal her full power over the winds unless playing with some who is able to keep up with her antics.
